snippet.textDisplay: Listening from Nepal Nov 1 2025. Didn't realised this songs lyrics were this touching. I am hooked. What I realised as I listen to this song in loop is this might be the greatest music and lyrics plus singers combination ever in human history ,the chills this song gives me even if i repeatedly listen is beyond my understanding. This starting verse gives me chills and the goosebumps don't know why every time and the lady nasebo lal, I searched her trying to listen to her other songs but didn't found any good but this one is magical and she deserves all the praise and accolades .take a bow .wow . Credit needs to be given where it is due . Absolutely magical and refreshing.❤
